---
title: Salmon in Creamy Dijon Chive Sauce with Roasted Potato Wedges & Lemony Asparagus
description: Looking for a meal that’s light, bright, and super satisfying? You’ve come to the right place! This dish is all that and then some. Salmon fillets are pan-seared until the skin gets nice and crisp, then served alongside roasted potatoes and lemony asparagus. For a dynamic finish, the salmon is drizzled with a creamy Dijon pan sauce. You’ll definitely want to keep this delicious recipe in your back pocket.
